{"tid":2345510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"封關截毒快狠準 台灣防疫之光","createTime":"2020-12-29T14:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T08:52:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5a2ced7b677d9d427fb78687044619d04c1e5327","tid":2345510,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:08:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201229/ZFSKKITXJZGDHJAF3VIOCD7YBY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201229%2FZFSKKITXJZGDHJAF3VIOCD7YBY%2F&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=4125cb8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201229%2FZFSKKITXJZGDHJAF3VIOCD7YBY%2F&h=d8ab13ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201229/ZFSKKITXJZGDHJAF3VIOCD7YBY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n封關截毒快狠準 台灣防疫之光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kJl8wVxd-oE405WT5w1FpqE_RqQ=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GEMC2IDCM5HOPK4ZQLWVEUGIOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkJl8wVxd-oE405WT5w1FpqE_RqQ%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGEMC2IDCM5HOPK4ZQLWVEUGIOY.jpg&h=0af7ba17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■抗疫有功的蔡英文獲《時代》選為風雲人物。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府防疫滯後以致疫症百般纏身，一海之隔的台灣則吸取了沙士經驗，疫情之初以快、狠、準決策，成功堵截病毒。時至本月，香港爆發第四波疫情，台灣已陸續舉辦演唱會、馬拉松比賽，生活重返正軌，就連世衞官員也稱讚，台灣是亞洲防疫成功典範。也令台灣因防疫成國際之光。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：擊潰環球經濟 218萬億化水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成立「國家隊」供應口罩<br />\n<br />\n今年1月底，美國約翰霍普金斯大學研究機構曾預測，台灣會是風險最高的國家之一。然而，台灣未如外界預期般淪陷。死亡率及確診率至今仍低得驚人，截至12月28日統計，累積793宗確診個案，其中本土個案56宗，確診個案7人死，死亡率僅0.8%。事實上，湖北武漢爆出不明肺炎時，台灣一早設立防線，去年12月31日，湖北武漢衞健委首次公佈不明肺炎訊息，行政院長蘇貞昌當日宣佈將大陸肺炎按照SARS處理，比其他國家早一步將武漢肺炎公告為「第五類法定傳染病」。<br />\n<br />\n各地口罩供應緊張，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有別港府對全面封關置若罔聞，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國NBC News總結台灣對抗武漢肺炎的關鍵，包括提前展開防疫措施；設置中央疫情指揮中心；果斷採取行動；違反隔離措施會被重罰。同時，兩大防疫功臣發揮關鍵作用，衞福部部長陳時中隨時滙報每日情況；數位（數碼）政務委員唐鳳利用「大數據分析」，完成口罩即時地圖及推行口罩實名制，讓市民能購買口罩「保命」。<br />\n<br />\n疫苗方面，官方也一早向市民派定心丸，9月宣佈與COVAX國際疫苗開發計劃簽約，11月已肯定獲1,500萬劑疫苗，預計2021年首季施打。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WbO8XbK17NsCnyb8wC_i6uou5yg=/1774x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UPQ5S3COURD55EMXSEPSEYESKA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWbO8XbK17NsCnyb8wC_i6uou5yg%3D%2F1774x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUPQ5S3COURD55EMXSEPSEYESKA.jpg&h=03e16b39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台灣「國家隊」製口罩惠及全球。"},{"pid":"fc004b4a422ea825d6469049bc86df07abd4bc83","tid":2345510,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:09:54.000Z","msg":"挑！<br />\n<br />\nNEW ZEALAND咪一樣<br />\n<br />\n你呢D大中華膠 (&amp; 毒果員工) 眼界係不能越過南中國海！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7d8845f8db2c245c1eb05abc7e9d8793c97671","tid":2345510,"uid":115847,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:10:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"pink\">love you english</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a268c5584a436183f3fe2eac79edad6ad3972954","tid":2345510,"uid":226955,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:15:10.000Z","msg":"Taiwan can help<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4696015e39ba2f9ee750d9ae821e9b8e05eab32e","tid":2345510,"uid":179729,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:16:24.000Z","msg":"范范：狗官"},{"pid":"10206a9258dc079619226239e4ee4d35c6e65657","tid":2345510,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,